#* {{quote-book|title=The history of England: from the accession of James the Second|volume=9|page=153|year=1861|author=[[w:Thomas Babington Macaulay|Thomas Babington Macaulay]]|passage=The two parties, after exchanging a good deal of '''abuse''', came to blows.}}

