===Etymology 2===
* First attested early 15th century. From {{etyl|frm}} {{term|abuser|lang=frm}}, from {{etyl|VL.}} {{term|abusare|lang=la}}, from {{etyl|la}} {{term|abusus|abūsus|lang=la}}, perfect active participle of {{term|abutor|abūtor|lang=la}}, from {{term|ab||from, away from|lang=la}} + {{term|utor|ūtor|use|lang=la}}.
* First attested use for perverse sexual activity in early 15th century.
* First attested use for sex abuse was in 1550's.
* First attested use for drug abuse was 1968.

